  <entry>
    <title>遇到的hexo报错</title>
    <link href="/2022/04/02/%E9%81%87%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84hexo%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99/"/>
    <url>/2022/04/02/%E9%81%87%E5%88%B0%E7%9A%84hexo%E6%8A%A5%E9%94%99/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>22-04-02：</p><p>碰到一个很蠢的报错， <code>type: 'expected variable end'</code> 原因是编写的md文件中有出现相连接的<code>&#123;</code>或<code>&#125;</code>，原因是连续的中括号会与配置文件发生一些冲突，避免编写公式时出现这种情况</p><p>或者是找到语句进行修改：</p><figure class="highlight latex"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><div class="code-wrapper"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></div></td><td class="code"><pre><code class="hljs latex">&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">% raw %&#125;//敏感内容前加上这个</span><br>Hello &#123;&#123; sensitive &#125;&#125;//敏感内容被包装在中间<br>&#123;<span class="hljs-comment">% endraw %&#125;//敏感内容后加上这个</span><br></code></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p>最简单的应该还是直接加空格了吧</p>]]></content>
    
    
    
    <tags>
      
      <tag>hexo</tag>
      
    </tags>
    
  </entry>
  
  
  
  <entry>
    <title>数字电路知识点</title>
    <link href="/2022/04/02/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E7%82%B9/"/>
    <url>/2022/04/02/%E6%95%B0%E5%AD%97%E7%94%B5%E8%B7%AF%E7%9F%A5%E8%AF%86%E7%82%B9/</url>
    
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>学习完数字电路部分知识点有些混乱，总结一下</p><p><code>正逻辑</code>(positive logic)，开关代数的基本概念之一，与门和或门的概念是相对，用1表示高电位，用0表示低电位；</p><h2 id="基础门电路">基础门电路</h2><p>三个基本门，非门也叫反相器</p><p>图中均有两种绘图形式，下方的为国内格式</p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">AND Gate 与门</th><th style="text-align: center;">OR Gate 或门</th><th style="text-align: center;">NOT Gate 非门(Inverter)</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315093443504.png" alt="image-20220315093443504" style="zoom: 33%;" /><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315093724372.png" alt="image-20220315093724372" style="zoom: 33%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315093640636.png" alt="image-20220315093640636" style="zoom: 33%;" /><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315093743329.png" alt="image-20220315093743329" style="zoom: 33%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315093843576.png" alt="image-20220315093843576" style="zoom: 33%;" /><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315093900668.png" alt="image-20220315093900668" style="zoom: 33%;" /></td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(Z = X·Y\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(Z = X+Y\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(Z = X&#39;\)</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p>其他常见的门：<strong>(注意记住咋画)</strong></p><table><colgroup><col style="width: 25%" /><col style="width: 25%" /><col style="width: 25%" /><col style="width: 25%" /></colgroup><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;">NAND Gate 与非门</th><th style="text-align: center;">NOR Gate 或非门</th><th style="text-align: center;">XOR Gate 异或门</th><th style="text-align: center;">XNOR Gate 同或门</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315102719809.png" alt="image-20220315102719809" style="zoom: 50%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315102820428.png" alt="image-20220315102820428" style="zoom: 50%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315104400166.png" alt="image-20220315104400166" style="zoom: 50%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220315104759295.png" alt="image-20220315104759295" style="zoom: 50%;" /></td></tr><tr class="even"><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(Z=(X \cdot Y)&#39;\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(Z=(X+Y)&#39;\)</span></td><td style="text-align: center;">$<span class="math display">\[\begin{align}\mathrm{Z}&amp;=\mathrm{X} \oplus \mathrm{Y}\\\end{align}\]</span> $</td><td style="text-align: center;"><span class="math inline">\(\begin{align}Z =&amp;\operatorname X \odot \operatorname{Y}=(\mathrm{X} \oplus \mathrm{Y})&#39;\\\end{align}\)</span></td></tr></tbody></table><p>其中<span class="math inline">\(\mathrm{X} \oplus \mathrm{Y}= X&#39;Y+XY&#39;,\operatorname X \odot \operatorname{Y}=XY+X&#39;Y&#39;\)</span></p><h2 id="组合逻辑设计原理">组合逻辑设计原理</h2><ul><li><p>单变量： <span class="math display">\[\begin{array}{lllll}\hline \text { (T1) } &amp; X+0=X &amp; (T 1&#39;) &amp; X \cdot 1=X &amp; \text { (自等律) } \\\text { (T2) } &amp; \color{red}X+1=1 &amp; (T 2&#39;) &amp; X \cdot 0=0 &amp; ( \text { 0-1律 }) \\\text { (T3) } &amp; X+X=X &amp; (T 3&#39;) &amp; X \cdot X=X &amp; \text { (同一律) } \\\text { (T4) } &amp; (X)^{\prime}=X &amp; &amp; &amp; \text { (还原律) } \\\text { (T5) } &amp; \color{red}X+X^{\prime}=1 &amp; (T 5&#39;) &amp; X \cdot X^{\prime}=0 &amp; \text { (互补律) } \\\hline\end{array}\]</span></p></li><li><p>双变量： <span class="math display">\[\begin{array}{lllll}\hline (T 8) &amp; X \cdot Y+X \cdot Z=X \cdot(Y+Z) &amp; (T 8&#39;) &amp; \color{red}(X+Y) \cdot(X+Z)=X+Y \cdot Z &amp; (\text { 分配律 }) \\(T 9) &amp; \color{red}X+X \cdot Y=X &amp; (T 9&#39;) &amp;\color{red} X \cdot(X+Y)=X &amp; (\text { 吸收律) } \\(T 10) &amp; X \cdot Y+X \cdot Y^{\prime}=X &amp; (T 10&#39;) &amp; \color{red}(X+Y) \cdot(X+Y&#39;)=X &amp; (\text { 组合律 }) \\(T 11) &amp; X \cdot Y+X^{\prime} \cdot Z+Y \cdot Z=X \cdot Y+X^{\prime} \cdot Z &amp; &amp; &amp; (\text { 添加律 }) \\(T 11&#39;) &amp; (X+Y) \cdot\left(X^{\prime}+Z\right) \cdot(Y+Z)=(X+Y) \cdot\left(X^{\prime}+Z\right) &amp; &amp; &amp; \\\hline\end{array}\]</span></p></li><li><p>n变量：<code>德摩根</code> $$</p><span class="math display">\[\begin{array}{lll}\hline  (T12)   &amp; X+X+\cdots+X=X  &amp; \text {(广义同一律)} \\(T12&#39;)  &amp; X\cdot X\cdots X=X  \\(T13)   &amp; ({X}_{1} \cdot {X}_{2} \cdot \cdots \cdot {X}_{n})^{\prime}={X}_{1}^{\prime}+{X}_{2}^{\prime}+\cdots+{X}_{n}^{\prime}  &amp; \text{(德摩根定理)}\\(T13&#39;)  &amp; ({X}_{1}+{X}_{2}+\cdots+{X}_{n})^{\prime}={X}_{1}^{\prime} \cdot {X}_{2}^{\prime} \cdots \cdots \cdot {X}_{n}^{\prime} \\\hline\end{array}\]</span><p>$$</p></li><li><p>异或同或关系：</p><p>n个异或(同或)门： <span class="math display">\[\begin{aligned}\mathrm{X}_{1} \oplus \mathrm{X}_{2} \oplus \cdots \oplus \mathrm{X}_{\mathrm{n}}=\left\{\begin{array}{ll}1 &amp; \text { Odd number of } 1 \mathrm{~s} \\ 0 &amp; \text { Even number of } 1 \mathrm{~s}\end{array}\right. \\\mathrm{X}_{1} \odot \mathrm{X}_{2} \odot \cdots \odot \mathrm{X}_{\mathrm{n}}=\left\{\begin{array}{ll}1 &amp; \text { Even number of } 0 \mathrm{~s} \\0 &amp; \text { Odd number of } 0 \mathrm{~s}\end{array}\right.\end{aligned}\]</span> 因果互换关系：<span class="math inline">\(\mathrm{X} \oplus \mathrm{Y}=\mathrm{Z} \rightarrow \mathrm{X} \oplus \mathrm{Z}=\mathrm{Y} \rightarrow \mathrm{Y} \oplus \mathrm{Z}=\mathrm{X}\)</span></p></li><li><p>对偶定理：</p><p>交换所有的<code>0</code>和<code>1</code>以及<code>"+"</code>和<code>"·"</code>，规则对倒</p><p><span class="math inline">\(F^{D}\left(X_{1}, X_{2}, \cdots, X_{n}, 0,1,+, \cdot\right)=F\left(X_{1}, X_{2}, \cdots, X_{n}, 1,0, \cdot,+,\right)\)</span></p></li></ul><h2 id="cmos门电路">CMOS门电路</h2><p>MOS管：<code>n型</code>为高通，<code>p型</code>为低通，对于相同的硅面积，n沟道晶体管的“导通”电阻比p沟道晶体管的要低</p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;"><strong>Inverter</strong> 反相器</th><th style="text-align: center;">NAND Gates与非门</th><th style="text-align: center;"><strong>NOR Gates</strong>或非门</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220323112330086.png" alt="image-20220323112330086" style="zoom: 50%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220323112913769.png" alt="image-20220323112913769" style="zoom: 40%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220323112934865.png" alt="image-20220323112934865" style="zoom: 45%;" /></td></tr></tbody></table><p>需要关注的地方在于A，B所连接的<code>n</code>型MOS管为串联还是并联，串联<code>(AB)</code>则导通两个才能导致Z的低电平，并联<code>(A+B)</code>则导通一个导致Z的低电平，对应与门的非和或门的非</p><p>基于等效门电路原理，看电路功能时可以最后在括号外加非</p><h3 id="门电路设计">门电路设计</h3><p>注意分功能来设计，分模块后拼接即可，因为门电路不能直接表示<code>与门</code>或者<code>或门</code>，以下给出总体功能模块：(主要学习的思路还是模块分层)</p><table><thead><tr class="header"><th style="text-align: center;"><strong>AND Gates</strong>与门</th><th style="text-align: center;"><strong>OR Gates</strong>或门</th></tr></thead><tbody><tr class="odd"><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220402004723236.png" alt="image-20220402004723236" style="zoom:50%;" /></td><td style="text-align: center;"><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220402004747060.png" alt="image-20220402004747060" style="zoom:50%;" /></td></tr></tbody></table><h2 id="fanin-fanout-扇入扇出">Fanin Fanout 扇入扇出</h2><p>门电路所具有的输入端的数目，称为该逻辑系列的扇入</p><p>一个<code>n</code>输入门就具有<code>n</code>个串联和<code>n</code>个并联晶体管</p><p>串联晶体管“导通”的电阻可加性限制了CMOS门的扇入数；NOR gates ≤ 4 NAND gates ≤ 6</p><h3 id="计算散出数">计算散出数</h3><p>高电平：HIGH - state fanout <span class="math display">\[{N}_{\mathrm{H}}=\vert \frac{  {I}_{\mathrm{OHmax} } }{ {I}_{\mathrm{IHmax} } }\vert\]</span> 低电平：LOW - state fanout <span class="math display">\[{N}_{L}=\vert \frac{ {I}_{\mathrm{OLmax} } }{ {I}_{\mathrm{ILmax} } }\vert \]</span> Overall fanout <span class="math inline">\(N=\min \left({N}_{\mathrm{H}}, {N}_{\mathrm{L}}\right)\)</span></p><p>Excess driving capability 剩余驱动能力：<span class="math inline">\(\left\{\begin{align} &amp;高电平:\quad \vert {I}_{ {O H { m a x } } }\vert -{N}\vert {I}_{ {I H m a x} }\vert \\ &amp;低电平 :\quad \vert {I}_{\mathrm{OLmax} }\vert -{N}\vert {I}_{\text {ILmax } }\vert &amp; \end{align}\right.\)</span></p><h2 id="noise-margins-噪声容限">noise margins 噪声容限</h2><p><img src="https://wuyaohui06022.oss-cn-chengdu.aliyuncs.com/img/image-20220324104313904.png" alt="image-20220324104313904" style="zoom: 33%;" /></p><p><span class="math inline">\(V_{NH} = V_{OHmin} – V_{IHmin}\qquad V_{NL} = V_{ILmax} – V_{OLmax}\)</span>，关键在于确认好输入<code>(drive)</code>输出<code>(load)</code></p>]]></content>
    
    
    
